28.2.122\n| accessdate = 2019-12-09}}</ref>\n| away = Marist\n| try1 = [[George Gardiner (rugby league)|George Gardiner]] 2, [[Frank Delgrosso]], Ward, Payne\n| con1 = [[Frank Delgrosso]] 3\n| pen1 = [[George Gardiner (rugby league)|George Gardiner]]\n| try2 = [[Charles Gregory (rugby league)|Charles Gregory]], Billy Ghent, [[Jack Kirwan (rugby league)|Jack Kirwan]], [[Andrew O\u2019Brien (rugby)|Jim O\u2019Brien]]\n| con2 = [[Charles Gregory (rugby league)|Charles Gregory]] 3\n| pen2 = [[Charles Gregory (rugby league)|Charles Gregory]] 2\n| stadium =Carlaw Park 1\n| attendance =\n| referee = Saunders\n}}\n\n======Final======\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 3 October\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 35-3\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Storming Memorial Shield/Ponsonby\u2019s Easy Win\n| page = 12\n| publisher = New Zealand Herald, Volume LXII, Issue 19140\n| date = 1925-10-05\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19251005.2.123.6\n| accessdate = 2019-12-09}}</ref>\n| away = City\n| try1 = [[George Gardiner (rugby league)|George Gardiner]] 4, [[Tim Peckham]] 2, Godley, S Riley, Payne\n| con1 = [[Frank Delgrosso]], [[Tim Peckham]]\n| pen1 = [[Frank Delgrosso]] 2\n| try2 = [[Lou Brown (rugby league)|Lou Brown]]\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 1\n| attendance =\n| referee = Taylor\n}}\n\n==Top Try Scorers and Point Scorers (Senior Grade and Roope Rooster)==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n!Rank!!Player!!Team!!Tries\n|-\n|1||[[Lou Brown (rugby league)|Lou Brown]]||City Rovers||17\n|-\n|2||[[Ivan Littlewood]]||Ponsonby United||16\n|-\n|3||Wardlaw||City Rovers||13\n|-\n|4||[[Frank Delgrosso]]||Ponsonby United||9\n|-\n|4||[[George Gardiner (rugby league)|George Gardiner]]||Ponsonby United||9\n|-\n|4||H Hawkes||City Rovers||9\n|-\n|4||[[Hec McDonald]]||City Rovers||9\n|-\n|8||Godley||Ponsonby United||8\n|-\n|8||Riley||Ponsonby United||8\n|-\n|8||Veart||Devonport Uni